    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-biofluid-lab-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for Model Risk Level 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 and are addressed qualitatively within assessed factors. The relative hemolysis index acceptance criterion RH < 1 is satisfied across all five COU operating points. The governing requirement (https://uofa.net/synth/req/vv40-2018-hemolysis-rh-criterion) references ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3 gradation thresholds and the RH < 1 comparative criterion, which remain the applicable regulatory benchmark. The 2026-Q1 model baseline incorporating revised impeller geometry tolerances is assessed as credible for the stated COU. Overall credibility assessment: Accepted.",
